---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Radiology Training" description="RANZCR clinical radiology training program overview.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Clinical Radiology Training</h1>
    <p>RANZCR — Royal Australian & New Zealand College of Radiologists</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-grid">
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">5</div><div class="stat-label">years total training program</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">3</div><div class="stat-label">training phases</div></div>
    <div class="stat"><div class="stat-number">4</div><div class="stat-label">maximum application attempts</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Training Phases</h2>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-title">Phase 1 — Foundation</div><p>Foundation knowledge and skills. Phase 1 Examinations: Anatomy + Applied Imaging Technology (written). Must pass to progress to Phase 2.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-title">Phase 2 — Development</div><p>Further development of abilities and breadth of practice. Minimum 24 months FTE before sitting Phase 2 written examination. Phase 2 exams: MCQ + Case Reporting + OSCER.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="card-title">Phase 3 — Consolidation</div><p>Consolidation of skills and focus on areas of interest. Requires minimum 48 months FTE (Phase 1 + 2 combined) to progress here.</p></div>
  </div>
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Quick Links</h2>
    <ul class="item-list">
      <li><a href="/radiology/entry">Entry requirements & application</a></li>
      <li><a href="/radiology/exams">Examinations — Phase 1 & Phase 2</a></li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</Layout>
